Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located in the heart of Woden
Plenty of amenity at your door step

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Cosmopolitan Centre is located in the heart of Woden with an abundance of amenity at your door step with direct access to Woden Plaza, Westfield & the bus interchange.  

The building has undergone a refurbishment with new central air-conditioning plant, carpet, ceiling, lighting as well as painting the exterior of the building giving it a modern face lift.  

Secure and public parking is readily available, the Cosmopolitan Centre provides you with the best value commercial space in Woden.

Available now:

Level 2: 98sqm* Warm shell open plan office space.

Level 3: 90sqm - 590sqm* Warm shell office/retail space with great exposure onto Woden Square.

Level 6 - 725sqm* Warm shell office space which can be subdivided to meet requirements.

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PROFESSIONAL OFFICE SPACE FOR SALE OR LEASE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Perfectly positioned and connected to Westfield Woden, 7 Neptune Street offers flexible corporate spaces suitable for a variety of professional businesses.  Amenity is readily available for occupiers with direct access to various food and beverage offerings, services and retail shopping.  

Situated in the Woden Town Center which has a strong Government presence, this location is well connected to Barton, City CBD, Deakin and a short distance to the Canberra Hospital.  Public transport is readily available as well as generous on site parking.

The building has undergone refurbishment works including a brand new lift, renewed entry foyer and directory board signage.  The floor plates will include refreshed amenity, new ceiling tiles and floor coverings.

Flexible floor plates are available allowing subdivisions of areas from 87sqm* up to whole floors of 324sqm*.  Available floors are.

Level 4 - 324sqm*
Level 3 - 324sqm*

WOTSO are in the building and can offer flex space if necessary.

For further information please contact the exclusive marketing agents. 

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FLEXIBLE OFFICE ACCOMMODATION LOCATED IN THE HEART OF WODEN

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
1 Bowes Place is situated in the heart of the Woden Town Centre.  The location has seen an influx of investment from major developers off the back of the announcement of Stage 2 of the light rail. The building itself is occupied by a mix of medical and office users.  The lifts have had a refresh and floors are wrapped with windows allowing good natural light. 

Bowes Place is on the doorstep of Westfield Woden, providing generous amenity for staff. Public transport is readily available as well as a large public car park out the front of the building.

Available for lease is a very unique penthouse office suite of 142sqm* featuring the following:

- Large private balcony with excellent overviews onto the inner south
- Shared male and female shower facilities on the ground floor
- Floor can be refurbished to meet current standards
- Owners can assist with fit out and create a space to meet requirements

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.

*Approx.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: High quality office and medical space

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
14 Furzer Street Phillip, Sky Park, is a landmark development situated in the heart of Phillip.  Surrounded by various government departments, it offers modern retail and office accommodation which is not easy to come by in the present market.   There is excellent amenity in close vicinity of the building for staff including Space Kitchen on the ground floor and a short walk to Westfield Woden & Hellenic Club Woden.  The Woden towncentre is experiencing significant growth making this the prime time to secure your space in this thriving location.

The building itself is an architectural achievement with extensive glass windows surrounding the ground and first floor.  The clever design makes it a true landmark building for the area hiding the 6 levels of car parking above the commercial suites.   Existing major tenants include the Department of Veterans Affairs and Sonic Healthcare.

Level 1 has the following availability:

Suite 2 - 251sqm* offering excellent natural light outlooking Furzer Street.
Suite 3 - 207sqm* ideal for a medical operator

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.
